BetterDesk is an AI powered interactive workbench that can see , understand and physically interact with the objects placed on it. Using multiple cameras , projection mapping, voice and gesture controls, custom built programmable motion surface , the desk can organise components, guide users through projects, visualize info directly on the workspace, and create interactive ways to build, learn and prototype. The core innovation is a custom active motion grid that allows objects to move across the desk without robotic arms, turning the workspace itself into an intelligent physical interface! 
